title: Gnomes used to tend to the waters of Hesli
content:
In the olden days, Gnomes helped to manage the waters and its animals. However, after @[The Draconic War](document:59bb8ea4-4e1f-4d47-9d3b-6761de8ac899), they moved onto land to break away from this past.

They still have great affinity with the waters, so they won't shy away from that.
